'''奧布瑞·克莉絲丁·普拉扎'''<ref name="bullett">{{Cite web |url=http://www.bullettmedia.com/article/aubrey-plaza-finally-confronts-her-multiple-personalities/ |title=Aubrey Plaza Finally Confronts Her Multiple Personalities |last=Plaza |first=Aubrey |date=2012-03-01 |website=Bullett Magazine |access-date=2016-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130119063607/http://bullettmedia.com/article/aubrey-plaza-finally-confronts-her-multiple-personalities/ |archive-date=2013-01-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>（{{lang-en|Aubrey Christina Plaza}}，{{bd|1984年|6月26日||}}<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2009/aug/03/entertainment/et-plaza3|title=Aubrey Plaza: Funny person|last=Olsen|first=Mark|date=August 3, 2009|newspaper=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|accessdate=2016-06-30|archive-date=2012-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103024553/http://articles.latimes.com/2009/aug/03/entertainment/et-plaza3|dead-url=no}}</ref>）是一名美國女演員和喜劇演員。她在《公園與遊憩》中飾演April Ludgate，之後，她又在幾部影片中擔任配角。2012年的喜劇《安全無保障》中是第一部由她出演主角的作品。

普拉扎因爲她實習生的經歷而進入了演藝圈。在正直的公民大隊劇院（Upright Citizens Brigade Theater）的[[即興劇場|即興]]和[[喜剧小品|喜劇小品]]中，她曾出演網路連續劇珍妮塔特秀（''Jeannie Tate Show''）。後來，她又在《[[命運好好笑|命運好好笑]]》（Funny People）、《[[歪小子史考特|歪小子史考特]]》（Scott Pilgrim vs. the World）等電影中出演角色。

== 早年 ==
普拉扎出生於[[特拉華州|特拉華州]][[威尔明顿_(特拉华州)|威爾名頓]]。她的母親叫做貝爾·納黛特，是名律師，她的父親則是大衛·普拉扎，從事金融顧問的工作<ref name="delawaretoday">{{Cite web|url=http://www.delawaretoday.com/Delaware-Today/March-2012/Aubrey-Plaza-of-NBCs-Parks-and-Recreation-Wilmington-Native-Is-Building-a-Buzz-in-Hollywood/|title=Aubrey Plaza of NBC’s Parks and Recreation: Wilmington Native Is Building a Buzz in Hollywood|author=John Micklos Jr.|date=February 16, 2012|publisher=Delaware Today|accessdate=2016-06-30|archive-date=2015-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923213442/http://www.delawaretoday.com/Delaware-Today/March-2012/Aubrey-Plaza-of-NBCs-Parks-and-Recreation-Wilmington-Native-Is-Building-a-Buzz-in-Hollywood/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="cormier">{{Cite web|url=http://blogs.delawareonline.com/pulpculture/2010/01/15/from-wilmy-to-hollywood/|title=From Wilmy to Hollywood|date=January 15, 2010|last=Cormier|first=Ryan|work=Delaware Online|publisher=[[The_News_Journal|The News Journal]]|accessdate=2016-06-30|archive-date=2017-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170422161029/http://blogs.delawareonline.com/pulpculture/2010/01/15/from-wilmy-to-hollywood/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/delawareonline/access/1941543461.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Jan+17%2C+2010&author=RYAN+CORMIER&pub=The+News+Journal&desc=Hey%2C+aren't+you+that+funny+girl%3F&pqatl=google|title=Hey, aren't you that funny girl?|accessdate=January 2, 2011|date=January 17, 2010|last=Cormier|first=Ryan|publisher=[[The_News_Journal|The News Journal]]}}</ref>。她有兩個妹妹，蕾妮和娜塔莉<ref name="delawaretoday"/>，後者是她擔任許多不同角色的靈感來源<ref name="latina">{{Cite web|url=http://www.latina.com/entertainment/tv/parks-recreation-star-aubrey-plaza-explains-why-shes-so-hot-right-now|title=''Parks & Recreation'' star Aubrey Plaza explains why she's so hot right now|date=April 9, 2009|last=Herrera|first=Monica|work=[[Latina_(magazine)|Latina]]|access-date=2016-06-30|archive-date=2012-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120618122858/http://www.latina.com/entertainment/tv/parks-recreation-star-aubrey-plaza-explains-why-shes-so-hot-right-now|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

普拉扎的名字來自Bread樂隊的一首歌曲，「Aubrey」<ref name="delawaretoday"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.blackbookmag.com/nightlife/track-list-aubrey-plaza-rocks-the-boat-1.21149|title=Tracklist: Aubrey Plaza Rocks the Boat - BlackBook|accessdate=January 2, 2011|date=March 11, 2012|publisher=Blackbookmag.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120216213740/http://www.blackbookmag.com/nightlife/track-list-aubrey-plaza-rocks-the-boat-1.21149|archivedate=2012年2月16日|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。普拉扎的父親是波多黎各人，而她的母親是爱爾蘭人和英國人的後代。<ref name="delawaretoday"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv-movies/girl-slouch-article-1.376882|title=This girl's no slouch|accessdate=January 2, 2011|author=Lee Hernández|date=June 11, 2009|publisher=Nydailynews.com|archive-date=2013-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130911081715/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv-movies/girl-slouch-article-1.376882|dead-url=no}}</ref>普拉扎這樣說：「在高中時代，我是唯一一個移民的後代，我是半個波多黎各人。我有一個大家庭，我的很多堂兄弟姊妹在波多黎各。」<ref name="latina"/>她參與了威爾明顿戲劇聯盟的製作。<ref name="delawaretoday"/>

